text: Mary Kelly (30 May 1907 - June 1986) was a British gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1986 deaths Category:British female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
